I"¿<p>Lorax is a Flutter application that helps people to be motivated to grow plants and trees. The user could track the progress of the growth of the tree, set reminders. gamify the process of planting trees and using social media platform to challenge peers on joining the movement todecrease carbon footprint of the world.</p>

<h2 id="tech-stack">Tech Stack</h2>

<p>Flutter
Firebase SDK</p>

<h2 id="boilerplate-features">Boilerplate Features:</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Login</li>
  <li>Database</li>
  <li>user notification</li>
</ul>

